<h2 id="3晋升大饼篇">3.晋升大饼篇</h2>

<p><strong>什么大饼，这是精神动力，来来来，我们一起走向行业巅峰</strong></p>

<p><img src="http://favorites.ren/assets/images/2019/it/heihua18.jpg" alt="" />
<img src="http://favorites.ren/assets/images/2019/it/heihua19.jpg" alt="" />
